    source
    theorem List.cons_ne_nil { : Type u_1} (a : ) (l : List ) :
    a :: l []
    source
    theorem List.cons_ne_self { : Type u_1} (a : ) (l : List ) :
    a :: l l
    source
    theorem List.head_eq_of_cons_eq :
    { : Type u_1} {h : } {t : List } {h : } {t : List }, h :: t = h :: t h = h
    source
    theorem List.tail_eq_of_cons_eq :
    { : Type u_1} {h : } {t : List } {h : } {t : List }, h :: t = h :: t t = t
    source
    theorem List.cons_inj { : Type u_1} (a : ) {l : List } {l' : List } :
    a :: l = a :: l' l = l'
    source
    theorem List.cons_eq_cons { : Type u_1} {a : } {b : } {l : List } {l' : List } :
    a :: l = b :: l' a = b l = l'
    source
    theorem List.exists_cons_of_ne_nil { : Type u_1} {l : List } :
    l [] (b : ), (L : List ), l = b :: L

    @[simp]

    List.length [a] = 1

    a l 0 < List.length l

    0 < List.length l (a : ), a l

    0 < List.length l (a : ), a l

    0 < List.length l (h : ), (t : List ), l = h :: t
    source

    0 < List.length l (h : ), (t : List ), l = h :: t
    source
    theorem List.exists_cons_of_length_succ { : Type u_1} {n : Nat} {l : List } :
    List.length l = n + 1 (h : ), (t : List ), l = h :: t

    theorem List.length_pos { : Type u_1} {l : List } :
    0 < List.length l l []

    (x : ), x l

    List.length l = 1 (a : ), l = [a]
